[normal]About Certsure[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Certsure LLP is the largest third party certification body in the UK for electrical contractors, with 36,000 regis
[normal]trants with either our NICEIC or
[normal] ELECSA brands. Though we launched in April 2013 as a joint venture between the Electrical Safety Council (ESC) and the Electrical Contractors’ Association (ECA), with the aim of providing funds for these organisations, our roots
[normal] and commitment to raising 
[normal]standards in the industry
[normal] date back 
[normal]112 years to 190
[normal]1
[normal]. 
