[normal]Our responses to questions raised by the Select Committee[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]1.[bold]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]T[bold]he extent to which members of the public are aware of the competent person scheme and that certain domestic electrical works need to be [bold]reviewed and certified to meet the requirements of Building Regulations[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1.1.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]We acknowledge that awareness of Part P amongst consumers requires improvement 
[normal]and 
[normal]t
[normal]hat is why 
