[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Government could commission a survey to provide a detailed picture of consumer awareness; however, a detailed survey would be 
[normal]costly. The ESC carries out an annual consumer survey that gauges consumer awareness of 
[normal]P
[normal]art 
[normal]P
[normal] and the need to use 
[normal]registered electrician
[normal]s
