[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.3.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]It is anticipated that the proposal will include all licensed Part P 
[normal]scheme operators
[normal] in England and Wales who meet the new scheme requirements in line with DCLG’s timeline, and would lead to the removal from the
[normal] market place of both existing registers (ElectricSafe Register and the El
[normal]ectrical Safety Register).
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]W
[normal]e 
[normal]have written to the 
[normal]Department
[normal] setting out our intentions and seeking Government support in this regard.
[normal]&#xa0;
